Senate Resolution 526
By: Senators Esteves of the 35th, Kemp of the 38th and Orrock of the 36th
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating Nicholas Dozier for winning the 2024-2025 GHSA Class A Division I Boys
2 State Basketball Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the BEST Academy boys basketball team has established and maintained a
4 proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
6 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
7 2025 campaign, the team captured its first-ever state championship; and
8 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
9 athletic ability, dedication, hard work, and unity of purpose and spirit of each member of the
10 team; its superb offensive and defensive talents; and the astute direction of coaches Brian
11 Weeden, Mario Lemons Sr., Damian Goodwin, and Jessica Johnson; and
12 WHEREAS, the team was further supported throughout the season by Managers ZaMya
13 Wallace and Taylor Roach'e as well as Athletic Trainer Lance Hibbert-Parrish; and
